data.description: Discover elegance and functionality in this inviting ranch home located within Morgan Township Schools, yes MORGAN TOWNSHIP! Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and vaulted ceilings, this residence offers a spacious and comfortable living environment. With a basement and finished loft, there's versatility for various lifestyle needs, whether it's additional living space, a home office, or recreational area. Situated on over a HALF ACRE underground electric fenced lot in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property provides ample outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. Perfectly suited for modern living, this home embodies both charm and practicality. Don't miss out on touring this beautiful home!
